<section id="Section519909">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>item sites</primary>
      <secondary>by item</secondary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>items</primary>
      <secondary>item site details for</secondary>
    </indexterm>Item Sites by Item</title>
  <para>To view Item Sites by Item, select the "Item Sites by Item" option.
  The following screen will appear:</para>
  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/dspItemSitesByItem.png" />
        </imageobject>
        <caption>Item Sites by Item</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>
  <para>When displaying Item Sites by Item, you are presented with the
  following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Item Number</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Enter the Item Number of the Item whose Item Site(s) you want to
        display. The browse button located to the right of the field leads to
        a searchable list of make and buy items.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>UOM</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Inventory Unit of Measure.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Show Inactive</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Select to display active as well as inactive Item Sites.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Item Sites</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Display lists Item Sites for the specified Item.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>To the far right of the screen, the following buttons are
  available:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>CLOSE</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
        desktop.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>QUERY</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Select to generate the display, using the specified
        parameters.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>PRINT</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>Right-clicking on an Item Site in the Item Sites list enables you to
  select the following menu options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <xi:include href="../supportfiles/rightclick.xml"
                xpointer="element(rightclickViewItemSite)"
                xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />
    <xi:include href="../supportfiles/rightclick.xml"
                xpointer="element(rightclickEditItemSite)"
                xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />
    <xi:include href="../supportfiles/rightclick.xml"
                xpointer="element(rightclickViewInventoryAvailability)"
                xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />
    <xi:include href="../supportfiles/rightclick.xml"
                xpointer="element(rightclickIssueCountTag)"
                xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />
    <xi:include href="../widgets/xtreewidget.xml"
                xpointer="element(xtreewidget.menu.exportcontents)"
                xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" />
  </variablelist>
</section>
